name: Hawaii: Part II Disc Display
desc:
This is a display piece for the album [Hawaii: Part II](https://miraclemusical.bandcamp.com/album/hawaii-part-ii) by [Miracle Musical](http://www.hawaiipartii.com/).

I tried to make the stella octangula be accurate, but had some issues trying to design it with the border. I like how it came out regardless :)
short_desc: This is a display piece for the album Hawaii: Part II by Miracle Musical.
